OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FSunak promises anti-social 
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fbehaviour crackdown        
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, People who vandalise public spaces will
OL,6, have to repair the damage they cause   
OL,7, within 48 hours of being given an      
OL,8, order, under new government plans.     
OL,10,FCommunities will also have a say on how
OL,11,Foffenders are punished, No 10 said.    
OL,13,FThe pilot, covering 10 areas, aims to  
OL,14,Fshow the public such acts are "quickly 
OL,15,Fand visibly" punished.                 
OL,17,FBut Labour accused the government of   
OL,18,F"slashing" neighbourhood policing and  
OL,19,Ftrying to copy their plan on "tough    
OL,20,Fcommunity payback".                    
